author: Reuters
title: TABLE-Pfizer India unit Q1 net profit jumps 42 pct y/y
text: MUMBAI, July 26 Three months ended June 30. (Versus the same period a year earlier. All Reuters alerts in billion rupees unless stated) Net profit: 0.54 vs 0.38 Net Sales: 4.8 vs 4.3 NOTE: Pfizer Ltd is the Indian unit of U.S. drugmaker Pfizer Inc. (Reporting by Rajendra Jadhav ; Editing by Paul Tait )
